RAIDERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
About all this nonsense of trying to get the Raiders to stay in Los Angeles: 
Expecting loyalty out of Al Davis is like expecting love out of a prostitute. 
If he doesn't leave now, he will as soon as you stop giving him presents. Grow 
up! 
</P>
<P>
GARY COYNE 
</P>
