12-point lead, 58-46. 
</P>
<P>
Washington forward Doug Meekins led a late surge that cut the lead to 60-54 
with 2:10 left. The Ducks came back as Brandon made a field goal and a free 
throw, and Keith Reynolds made two more free throws. 
