operating loss from the Olympic paints and stain business, which was sold. The 
company said total shipments of its products -- including Clorox liquid bleach, 
Liquid plumr drain opener, Match Light and BBQ Bag charcoal briquettes and 
Hidden Valley Ranch bottled salad dressing -- were up. 
