four apiece in an 11-2 spurt to put Arizona ahead to stay at 43-36 with 12:57 
left. After Arizona State closed to 49-45 with 10:06 to play, Williams had a 
jumper and two free throws in an 8-0 run to make it 57-45 with 6:52 left. 
</P>
