after the jury verdicts were read. ; Photo, Peggy McMartin Buckey embraces 
Daniel Davis, her son's attorney, in the courthouse hallway after the 'not 
guilty' verdicts were read. RICK MEYER / Los Angeles Times; Photo, WILLIAM R. 
POUNDERS; Photo, RAY BUCKEY; Photo, PEGGY MCMARTIN BUCKEY; Photo, LAEL R. 
RUBIN; Photo, ROGER J. GUNSON; Photo, DANIEL G. DAVIS; Photo, DEAN R. GITS 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
